title: MNF Recap, Mike Holmgren joins the show
itunes:title: MNF Recap, Mike Holmgren joins the show
description:
DJ and Bucky recap the Giants win over the 49ers on Monday Night (1:40), look ahead to the potential in next year’s draft (5:45). Then, the guys interview Super Bowl winning head coach Mike Holmgren (11:15). Plus, they close with a chat recapping Week 11 of college football (29:00).
